# Legacy pkgit-style dependency hints. Elda's importer (`elda a <repo>` /
# `elda rc add --import pkgit ./<repo>`) consumes this format and emits an
# Elda-native pkg.lua skeleton with a metadata-review gate before write.
#
# Lines are `<git-url> [optional-ref]`. Comments start with `#`.

